ABOUT_US
Your_Saturdays in Saigon just got a whole lot better !
Saigon_Soul has become an institution for many expats , locals and travellers as the liveliest pool party in the city . Our pool and dayclub are located in the heart of District 1 , at the New_World_Saigon_Hotel . Every_Saturday from November 28th , 2015 until May 14th , 2016 , you ’ ll enjoy the finest DJs that Saigon has to offer at our luxurious pool . From 10am to 10pm we ’ ve created a tempting cool oasis from the hot Saigon sun . You ’ ll be guaranteed a sexy , water fueled event with some fantastic house music and amazing people . What better way to spend a Saturday ?
The ultimate in poolside entertainment , Saigon_Soul is defined by its great party atmosphere . The pool is one of the largest in Saigon , featuring 25 sunbeds , a multitude of tables & chairs , 30 cushy bean bags and our highly acclaimed , 5 VIP cabanas . Electrifying beats by our world class DJs set a lively mood as you bask in the ambiance . Multiple bars and our mouthwatering menus will have you and the other 500 + Saigon_Soul party people coming back week after week . Things can ’ t get much better than this .
Upscale and chic , yet , down , dirty and outright affordable . We pride ourselves in not breaking your bank account with drinks starting at a mere 50,000 vnd . If you want to splash around with some high end spirits and champagne , our vast drink menu will accommodate your most refined tastes . Booming house music , drink specials , local restaurant food stations , giveaways , hotel promotions , swimwear retailers , beautiful people , a lovely pool with cold drinks , fun people and notorious good times . What are you waiting for ? See you poolside !
